{"type":"message","id":"cc3a82c4","parentId":"6698c2bb","timestamp":"2026-03-30T21:48:38.520Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" The user is just providing more system specs (64-bit OS, x64 processor). This is just additional information about their system, but not really adding to the conversation about autoresearch.\n\nI already created the pattern demo for them. Let me acknowledge the system info briefly but steer back to the actual question - what do they want to do next?","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"     Alles klar – 64-bit System passt perfekt für alles, was wir machen könnten.\n\n## Zusammenfassung was wir haben\n\n| Hardware | Status |\n|----------|--------|\n| CPU | i7-6820HK ✓ |\n| RAM | 32 GB ✓ |\n| GPU | GTX 980M 8GB ⚠️ (knapp, aber testbar) |\n| Storage | 932 GB SSD ✓ |\n| OS | 64-bit ✓ |\n\n## Deine Optionen jetzt\n\n**A) Pattern verstehen** ✅ (haben wir)\n- Demo liegt in `~/.openclaw/workspace/autoresearch-demo/`\n- Du kannst das für deine eigenen Skills adaptieren\n\n**B) Echtes Training testen** (experimentell)\n- Windows-Fork clonen\n- Parameter für 8GB anpassen\n- Einen Test-Run machen (wird langsamer sein, aber könnte gehen)\n\n**C) Auf Google Colab ausweichen**\n- Kostenlos, bessere GPU (T4 mit 16GB)\n- Einfach: Notebook öffnen, loslegen\n\n**D) Weiter mit was anderem**\n- Dieses Pattern auf einen deiner Skills anwenden?\n\nWas zieht dich an?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"kimi-k2-thinking","usage":{"input":1786,"output":357,"cacheRead":21952,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24095,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774907306426}}
