{"type":"message","id":"ec7313ad","parentId":"aa4c6911","timestamp":"2026-03-30T23:18:35.000Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" Perfekt! Ich habe die Top 10 Dateien. Besonders interessant:\n1. context-switch.ps1 (22.7 KB) - bereits analysiert vom Subagent\n2. sync-openclaw-to-obsidian.ps1 (22.1 KB) - Sync-Funktionalität\n3. MermaidGenerator.psm1 (22 KB) - Diagramm-Generierung\n4. DataviewQuery.psm1 (20.5 KB) - Datenbank-Queries\n5. Encryption.psm1 (18.3 KB) - Verschlüsselung\n6. auto-backup.ps1 (17.2 KB) - Backup-Funktion\n7. ecc-stability.ps1 (15.5 KB) - Stabilitätsprüfung\n8. cmd-backup.ps1 (15 KB) - Command-Backup\n9. eval-runner.ps1 (14.6 KB) - **WICHTIG: \"eval\" im Namen!**\n10. SecureCredential.psm1 (13 KB) - Credential-Handling\n\nDie Datei \"eval-runner.ps1\" ist besonders verdächtig wegen des Namens. Lass mich die kritischsten Dateien lesen.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"     **Top 10 PowerShell-Dateien gefunden!** Besonders interessant: `eval-runner.ps1` 😬\n\nLass mich die kritischsten Dateien prüfen:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_CFZOy6NpvtRhEtAqQTzdPGOz","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:/Users/andre/Documents/Andrew Openclaw/Kimi_Agent_ECC-Second-Brain-Framework Implementiert/scripts/eval-runner.ps1"}},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_IAtGBfwivPXrariFMcuwy9KC","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:/Users/andre/Documents/Andrew Openclaw/Kimi_Agent_ECC-Second-Brain-Framework Implementiert/modules/Encryption.psm1"}},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_8wDWjsjaMRQ7VyI8EtP5HXcC","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:/Users/andre/Documents/Andrew Openclaw/Kimi_Agent_ECC-Second-Brain-Framework Implementiert/modules/SecureCredential.psm1"}},{"type":"text","text":"  "}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"kimi-k2-thinking","usage":{"input":45544,"output":415,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45959,"cost":{"in