n\n---\n\n## 🎯 Gesamtergebnis\n\n| Komponente | Test | Status |\n|------------|------|--------|\n| **Safety-Checker** | Guter Code | ✅ PASS (95/100) |\n| **Safety-Checker** | Böser Code | ❌ BLOCKED (0/100) |\n| **Obsidian-Sync** | 10 Experimente | ✅ SYNCED |\n| **Obsidian-Sync** | Dashboard | ✅ CREATED |\n\n**→ Beide Tools funktionieren wie erwartet!** 🎉\n\n---\n\nSind wir jetzt **endgültig fertig**? 😊"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"kimi-k2-thinking","usage":{"input":130202,"output":717,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130919,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774915727051}}
