{"type":"message","id":"ecc87f0c","parentId":"8bc1858a","timestamp":"2026-03-31T02:24:50.855Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"   Ich muss den neuen Text angeben. Lass mich die neuen Learnings anhängen.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"tool_jcUwXap0aht9NvvQE5ULgWrh","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\n\n---\n\n## Additional Learnings (04:23 Update)\n\n### Complete PowerShell Error Patterns for German Windows Systems:\n\n1. **Whitespace in Cmdlets:** `SetEnvironmentVar iable` caused by line breaks → Use contiguous strings without spaces\n2. **Reserved Variables:** `$host` is reserved → Use `$hostname` instead\n3. **Unicode/Encoding:** Emojis cause \"string not terminated\" errors → Use ASCII-only: `[INFO]`, `[OK]`, `[WARN]`\n4. **Locale Dependencies:** \"Administrators\" vs \"Administratoren\" → Use SIDs like `S-1-5-32-544` or `$env:USERNAME`\n5. **Here-Strings:** Closing `\"@` must be at line start → Use one-liners for JSON\n6. **Permission Order:** Files copied before permissions set → Correct: takeown → icacls → copy\n7. **Missing Error Handling:** Scripts showed SUCCESS despite failures → Use `Test-Path` after operations\n8. **icacls Quotes:** Issues with usernames containing spaces → Use hardcoded usernames without spaces\n9. **takeown Locale:** `/D Y` doesn't work on German systems → Use `/D J` or interactive mode\n10. **Markdown Backticks:** Copied with code → Explicitly copy only text between backticks\n\n### Working Sequence (After 4 Hours - Only One That Worked):\n```powershell\ntakeown /F \"C:\\Path\" /R\n# Press J when prompted\nicacls \"C:\\Path\" /grant \"username:(OI)(CI)F\" /T\ncopy \"source\" \"dest\"\n'{\"key\":\"value\"}' | Set-Content \"config.json\"\n```\n\n**Final Status:** All solutions documented. Implementation ready for tomorrow with fresh mind.\n","path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-31.md"}},{"type":"text","text":"  "}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding"