{"type":"message","id":"3a92e949","parentId":"dd451c40","timestamp":"2026-03-31T23:31:32.802Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" The user is pointing out that they need to modify prepare.py as well. Let me acknowledge this and add it to the memory documentation.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"   ✅ Auch wichtig! `prepare.py` muss angepasst werden.\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 Änderungen in `prepare.py`:\n\n```python\n# Zeile ~23: MAX_SEQ_LEN reduzieren\nMAX_SEQ_LEN = 512  # Statt 2048\n\n# Zeile ~24: Eval-Tokens anpassen  \nEVAL_TOKENS = 10 * 524288  # Statt 40 * 524288\n```\n\n**Warum?** Weniger VRAM-Verbrauch für Tokenization!\n\n---\n\n## 📋 Vollständige Änderungsliste (GTX 980M):\n\n| Datei | Zeile | Original | Änderung |\n|-------|-------|----------|----------|\n| `train.py` | ~19 | `TOTAL_BATCH_SIZE = 2**19` | `2**15` |\n| `train.py` | ~42 | `DEPTH = 8` | `6` |\n| `train.py` | ~161 | `torch.bfloat16` | `torch.float32` |\n| `prepare.py` | ~23 | `MAX_SEQ_LEN = 2048` | `512` |\n| `prepare.py` | ~24 | `EVAL_TOKENS = 40*524288` | `10*524288` |\n\n---\n\nSoll ich das **vollständige Änderungs-Set** in MEMORY.md ergänzen? Dann hast du beim Wiederaufnehmen alles an einem Ort! 📝"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi-coding","model":"kimi-k2-thinking","usage":{"input":190595,"output":342,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":190937,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774999870688}}
